msgstr "以下命令可以列出 Xinference 中正在運行的模型："

#: ../../source/models/index.rst:146
msgid ""
"When you no longer need a model that is currently running, you can remove it"
" in the following way to free up the resources it occupies:"
msgstr "當你不再需要當前正在運行的模型時，以下列方式釋放其佔用的資源："

#: ../../source/models/index.rst:170
msgid ""
"For models that are no longer maintained and depend on outdated libraries "
"(such as ``transformers``), we recommend enabling the :ref:`Model Virtual "
"Environment <model_virtual_env>` feature to ensure they can run properly in "
"a compatible environment."
msgstr ""
"對於不再維護且依賴舊版庫（如 ``transformers`` ）的模型，建議啟用 :ref:`模型虛擬空間 <model_virtual_env>` "
"功能，以確保它們能在相容的環境中正常運作。"

